     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="11"/>
   <head>Another of the same.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>AS in the <hi>Sacrifices</hi> of the Law,</l>
      <l>there was an <hi>Alter, Priest Host, Fire</hi> and <hi>Wood:</hi>
      </l>
      <l>So <hi>This</hi> to <hi>That,</hi> in likenesse neere doth draw;</l>
      <l>and wants but holy-<hi>Fire</hi> to make it good.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>The <hi>Alter,</hi> is my <hi>Hope</hi>; the <hi>Host,</hi> my <hi>Heart</hi>;</l>
      <l>the <hi>Priest,</hi> my <hi>Faith</hi>; my <hi>Loue,</hi> the <hi>Fu<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>ll</hi> is:</l>
      <l>All these (ô Lord) are ready; but the Art</l>
      <l>to fire the <hi>Fuell,</hi> wants; then, doe thou This.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>I am but <hi>Passiue</hi> in this holy Act,</l>
      <l>Thou the sole <hi>Agent</hi>: yet, ô make me fi<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>
      </l>
      <l>To worke with thee together in this <hi>Fact,</hi>
      </l>
      <l>with all the Forces of my <hi>Will</hi> and <hi>Wit</hi>:</l>
      <l>And sith (deare <gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>o<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>d) all things so ready be,</l>
      <l>Giue <hi>Fire,</hi> to sacrifice my <hi>Heart</hi> to <hi>Thee!</hi>
      </l>
   </lg>
</div>
